instance: A dull head in the middle of windy expanses.
A fine pedantic ray of sunshine in a satin vest
Silence fills the story and gentleness fills the narrator's gaze
And the storm must be bad
But pale and thin because of the water The harmless feet still shine
Every street lamp I pass Beats like a fatalistic drum
Hope is the thing with feathers that sits in the soul and sings the melody without words and never stops
I do not spoil the beauty by being silent
I heard it in the coolest country
The heart of the ocean is too smooth too blue
The memory comes From sunless dry geraniums
The yellow mist rubbing its back against the window panes
The yellow smoke rubbing its mouth against the window panes
Under a windy button.
Where worried bodies of drowned men float down in the green silence
a crow flying in the sweetest air in heaven
A woman's face painted by nature's hand
like sweet showers of rain on the ground
Hide your bravery in their foul smoke
calmed the shrunken seas
kiss the green meadows with a golden face
The beauty of my sweet love
Sometimes it is too hot, the eye of the sky shines
that sweet smell
the bottom of quiet seas.
the sessions of sweet silent thoughts
the wide world and all its fading sweets
Its substance still lives sweetly
Listening with your eyes is part of the subtle joke of love
Give your sweet looks to someone else
